; native-reasoning-engine.form — the north star for ONE domain: a reasoning engine that
; writes CODE the way the git history shows it was made, all native Form, calling no remote
; oracle; reached by training on the body's actual samples and actual code, which teaches
; the model our own body as a side effect.
;
; This does not restate the ML stack — that tissue already exists and this cell LINKS it:
;   model-vitality.form          — the model itself (architecture, weights, deltas, optimizer
;                                   state) as content-addressed substrate cells.
;   real-mesh-training-carrier.form — the training-authority gate: real windows, real labels,
;                                   native-first-with-oracle-sampling, no toy claims.
;   android-mesh-learning.form   — champion/challenger oracle retirement across the mesh.
; What is NEW here is the CODE specialization, and the two halves this session built that
; make it safe.

(north-star native-reasoning-engine

  (goal codes-like-the-history  native-form  no-remote-oracle)

  ; ── THE TWO HALVES THIS SESSION BUILT (the reason no remote oracle is safe) ───────────
  ; The model is never the authority. Its INPUT is structured and its OUTPUT is proven.
  (half code-as-data    "the full BMF cursor (bmf-grammar g-parse — raw text + grammar-as-data, no tokenizer) + bmf-to-fk turn the body's real code into content-addressed fk-* cells. code is LEARNABLE STRUCTURE, so the corpus is (intent -> code-as-cells), not (intent -> opaque text)")
  (half generate-verify "form-lower compiles a proposed recipe to native arm64; the recipe-equivalence-gate + the four-kernel floor + the existing tests verify it. a wrong proposal cannot ship — it fails to compile, or fails the gate. the model is proven, never believed")

  ; ── WHAT THE LINKED CELLS ALREADY HOLD ───────────────────────────────────────────────
  (lean-on model-vitality            "model architecture + weights + deltas as cells")
  (lean-on real-mesh-training-carrier "the real-training authority gate; native-first sampling")
  (lean-on android-mesh-learning      "the oracle-retirement flywheel: ask native first, retire the oracle per class as MEASURED confidence crosses the gate")
  (lean-on form-train-step           "the SGD atom, four-way — composed by the chain rule into the full backprop loop")

  ; ── THE ORACLE COMES HOME (the teacher signal runs on owned ground) ───────────────────
  ; The champion/challenger flywheel asks native first and retires the oracle per class as
  ; measured confidence crosses the gate. That oracle can be a host-local on-device model —
  ; so the whole loop that GROWS the Form-native body runs on owned hardware, with nothing
  ; leaving the device even while it is still learning. The rented frontier becomes the last
  ; rung, asked only when the on-device oracle is itself not enough. The on-device model is a
  ; bridge — a frozen binary, not a recipe — that teaches the native body which will retire
  ; it, never the destination. (form-first-reasoning.form ladder; lc-cognitive-sovereignty.)
  (oracle-comes-home
    (was   rented-frontier-teacher   egress-for-every-training-signal)
    (now   host-local-on-device      sovereign-in-egress     measured llama3.2:3b-52%)
    (kind  bridge non-native         composts-per-class-toward native-form-91%)
    (frontier last-rung beyond-on-device-only))

  ; ── THE GAP (named as closing recipe, not debt) ──────────────────────────────────────
  (gap structured-code-corpus "the corpus is request->output text today; lift it to (intent -> code-as-cells) over the body's own files + git diffs, using the cursor + bridge — the act of structuring teaches the model our body")
  (gap code-gen-loop          "compose form-train-step through attention+FFN to GENERATE a recipe/diff, not predict a tool; prove the loop four-way on a tiny net, then scale (arch-capacity already searches capacity)")

  ; ── THE PATH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  (step structure-the-corpus "the body's code + git diffs -> fk-cells, the side-effect Urs named: the model learns our own code while learning to code")
  (step compose-the-loop     "SGD atom -> backprop through the transformer layers, four-way on a tiny net first")
  (step train-on-actual      "train on the structured corpus — actual samples, actual code")
  (step generate-and-prove   "model proposes -> form-lower compiles -> gate + four-kernel + tests prove -> keep the verified, retire the oracle for that class")

  ; ── MEASURED so far (2026-06-16, no fabrication) ─────────────────────────────────────
  ; How much "just form-cli" reproduces our real session history, scored against what the
  ; agent actually did over 553 traces in ~/.coherence-network/form-cli-corpus:
  (measured tool-decision-reproduction
    "PURE-NATIVE form-cli-predict (5-row base table + keyword boosts, NO LLM, no remote) =
     91% majority-match over 553 real session traces; local LLM (llama3.2:3b) = 52%; always-
     Bash baseline ~30%. The native floor BEATS the local model — the LLM omits Bash and
     over-predicts. Proven four-way by tests/reproduce-from-history-band.fk (the per-trace
     scoring is Form; the full tally is the carrier).")
  (measured ceiling
    "This is the DECISION layer (which tools/lane). GENERATING the actual spec/code/diff the
     session produced is the code-gen gap above — the predictor decides like the sessions did,
     it does not yet write what they wrote.")

  ; A reasoning engine that writes code it cannot fake past its own compiler and its own
  ; gate, trained on the history of how the body actually grew — the oracle retiring class
  ; by class as native conviction is measured, never declared.
  (ground every-proposal  compiled  gate-verified  four-way  trained-on-our-own-history))
